 Sigrid 分享新单曲“Ghost”并宣布推出 EP“The Hype” https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigrid-shares-new-single-ghost-and-announces-the-hype-ep-3510610?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sigrid-shares-new-single-幽灵并宣布炒作EPAlex Rigotti Fri, 06 Oct 2023 11:05:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3510610 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西格丽德（图片来源：Petros）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我希望这些歌词能让你读起来感到舒适，旋律让你想重复听”</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigrid-shares-new-single-ghost-and-announces-the-hype-ep-3510610">Sigrid 分享了新单曲“Ghost”，并宣布 EP“The Hype”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西格丽德（图片来源：Petros）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Sigrid-Ghost-Lead-Press-Shot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sigrid">西格丽德 (Sigrid)</a>宣布了她的新 EP“The Hype”，并分享了 EP“Ghost”中的一首新单曲。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sigrid-cover-interview-2021-mirror-sucker-punch-3011985"><strong>西格丽德接受采访：“当我现场演奏时，我的一部分就会显现出来——这是我的超能力”</strong></a></li></ul><p>这位挪威歌手（全名 Sigrid Solbakk Raabe）去年八月<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigrid-returns-with-questioning-new-single-the-hype-listen-3481710">带着 EP 的主打歌《The Hype》回归</a>。该专辑是她 2022 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sigrid-how-to-let-go-review-3219178">《How To Let Go》</a>的延续，该专辑获得了<em>NME 的四星评价，</em>被描述为“一张关于拥抱生活的混乱和矛盾荣耀的专辑”和“如此对生活的肯定”。</p><p>今天（10 月 6 日），Sigrid 通过 Island Records 透露《The Hype》EP 将于 10 月 27 日发行，并分享了有关该 EP 的更多细节。</p><p> “从我记事起，我就喜欢一切朗朗上口的东西，尤其是那些让你无法忘怀的旋律，”她说。 “它是什么类型并不重要，只要我想重复播放即可。难怪我开始制作流行音乐！我从来没有真正想过制作一种类型的流行歌曲，我只是想写好歌。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="西格丽德 - 幽灵（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mat0ATeA92Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她继续说道：“我一直在写作，我觉得今年发行一首单曲还不够，所以我决定发行一张 EP 来展示我现在的音乐水平。我喜欢这种形式：简短而活泼，但有足够的时间来展示歌曲创作、故事和声音的不同侧面。</p><p> “在《The Hype》EP 中，我写过关于想知道你是否真的没有辜负期望、搞砸、忘记某人，然后：你会没事的！我希望这些歌词能让你读起来感到舒适，旋律让你想重复听。”</p><p>找到下面的专辑封面和曲目列表： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CyDTQvStYyE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" b