索尼黑客攻击导致近7000名员工个人信息泄露https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-hack-causes-leak-of-nearly-7000-employees-personal-information-3510597?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sony-hack-causes-近7000名员工个人信息泄露Imogen DonovanFri, 06 Oct 2023 10:44:25 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3510597 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>索尼正在积极支持受影响的人</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-hack-causes-leak-of-nearly-7000-employees-personal-information-3510597">索尼黑客事件导致近 7,000 名员工的个人信息泄露</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sony-hack-exposed-7000-employees-data-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony">索尼</a>正在通过信用监控和身份恢复服务为因今年早些时候的网络攻击而泄露个人信息的 6,791 名员工提供支持。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950">以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>尽管“不知道”个人信息被公开或滥用，但索尼在 6 月份聘请了外部网络安全专家来了解泄露的程度。它还寻求执法部门的协助。</p><p> <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/sony-confirms-data-breach-impacting-thousands-in-the-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bleeping Computer</a>的报告声称，这是勒索软件团伙 Clop 所为，他们能够“[利用] MOVEit Transfer 平台中的零日漏洞”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3504444" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3504444" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3504444" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2.jpg" alt="索尼黑客" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/sony-reportedly-hacked-by-ransomed.vc-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3504444" class="wp-caption-text">黑暗房间中的一台笔记本电脑，屏幕上显示一行行代码 图片来源：Markus Spiske，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> MOVEit 是开发商 Progress Software 开发的文件传输程序，该程序于 5 月 31 日攻击三天后向用户通知了该漏洞。</p><p>随后，索尼意识到自己受到了 Clop 的攻击，并“立即”将 MOVEit 下线，以调查此次黑客攻击造成的破坏程度。</p><p>尽管无法确定该事件的具体日期，但<a href="https://apps.web.maine.gov/online/aeviewer/ME/40/8b595be6-d1d7-47df-84d5-05738edd84f9.shtml" target="_blank" rel="noopener">缅因州总检察长办公室</a>证实，索尼 6,791 名员工的姓名和社会安全号码在此次安全漏洞中被删除。</p><p> 9 月，索尼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-is-investigating-claims-that-all-of-its-systems-have-been-hacked-3504374">再次遭受另一个勒索软件组织的攻击</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3465133" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3465133" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3465133" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/playstation-5-ps5-sony-ps5-slim-handheld-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3465133" class="wp-caption-text"> PlayStation 5 图片来源：Triyansh Gill，来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> Ransomed.vc 自称是“数字和平税领域的领先公司”，并试图恐吓公司为被盗的敏感文件支付赎金，而不是向监管机构支付数据保护罚款。</p><p>该组织没有具体说明从黑客攻击中获得了什么信息，但索尼“目前正在调查情况”，并补充说“目前没有进一步评论”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em>《恐龙领主》</em>是一款即将推出的历史模拟游戏，它<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dino-lords-is-a-new-strategy-game-with-dinosaur-riding-vikings-3509909">想象了另一个时间线，斯堪的纳维亚人在维京人入侵英国时使用恐龙</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sony-hack-causes-leak-of-nearly-7000-employees-personal-information-3510597">索尼黑客事件导致近 7,000 名员工的个人信息泄露</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
